name: Running w/ Ryan. We got lost
description: Went off down the parkway and turned right on Honey Creek instead of the usually left. Explored some new trails. Ended up running in a dried up paved river bed for a while. Definitely slow, but good to catch up, get some easy miles, and happy with how my ankle handles the 7 miles of uneven surfaces.
